      • choosePeriod

        private int choosePeriod()
        Choose a period for graph's Timeline, appropriated to population size it helps to reduce workload on threads for big size populations
        Returns:
        100 ms for small populations and 500 ms for big ones

      • launchDrawGraph

        private void launchDrawGraph()
        Timeline launcher for drawing the graphs in AreaChart To show correctly superposed layers in AreaChart we take:
        • NbHealthy taken as 100% (bottom layer)
        • nbSick = nbSick + NbIncubating + nbRecovered (middle layer)
        • NbRecovered = NbRecovered (top layer)
        Superposed they present ratio of these tree values (nbHealthy, nbSick/Incubating and nbRecovered) in 100%

      • drawPoint

        private void drawPoint​(CoquilleBille cb,
                       boolean is_panel1,
                       double koeffW,
                       double koeffH)
        Renderer of points. Function which:
        • adapt position in GUI's Pane relative to position in Model's Zone
        • draw point according its status (Healthy, Sick, Recovered, Incubating)
        Parameters:
        is_panel1 - serves to distinguish drawing in Panel1 and Panel2 and its populations.
        koeffW - , koeffH serve to adapt dimensions the walls during changing dimensions the scene.
